# Cold Start Strategy

## Problem

New channels have:

- No engagement history
- No audience data
- No performance trends

## Solution

Bootstrap using:

- Competitor intelligence
- Industry benchmarks
- Merchant seasonality
- Category behavior patterns

Then gradually shift to:

> Channel-specific learning

---

# Growth Phases

## Phase 1 — Zero Data (Day 0–7)
- Competitor-driven strategy
- High-frequency experimentation
- Broad category testing

## Phase 2 — Pattern Discovery (Day 7–30)
- Identify high-performing content types
- Remove weak formats
- Optimize posting schedule

## Phase 3 — Optimization (30+ Days)
- Personalized predictions
- Automated planning
- Growth forecasting

