# Success Criteria

The Growth Engine is successful when:

- New channels achieve early traction faster than manual strategies
- Posting strategy improves within 7 days of launch
- Competitor intelligence directly influences growth decisions
- Channel-specific learning replaces generic benchmarks over time
- Users rely on AI suggestions for daily posting decisions

